title: Free Fall Through Time (Party Version)
info:
Written for the Sunrise 2011 Music Compo

        Complete song written in about 20 hours just 
        right before the compo deadline. It's labelled 
        the "party" version because I could not stuff 
        all of my ideas into 4 minutes of music. Still 
        I'm quite pleased with the result and I hope 
        you will be too! :)
